TO BUILD AND INSTALL THIS LIBRARY FROM A SOURCE TARBALL (.tgz), do

   ./configure [--prefix={path where you want to install}]
   make
   make install
   
TO BUILD AND INSTALL FROM A BAZAAR BRANCH, do

   autoreconf -ivf
   ./configure [--prefix={path where you want to install}]
   automake --add-missing
   ./configure [--prefix={path where you want to install}]
   make
   make install
